<div
  style="
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #1f2937;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 15px;
  "
>
  <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0f172a; font-size: 20px">
    Application for Senior React Developer
  </h2>

  <p>Dear <strong><%= hiringManagerName || 'Hiring Manager' %></strong>,</p>

  <p>
    My name is <strong><%= senderName %></strong>. I am applying for the
    position of <strong>Senior React Developer</strong>. I have
    <strong><%= experienceYears %> years</strong> of experience in building
    modern, scalable web applications using <strong>React.js</strong>,
    <strong>Next.js</strong>, and frontend best practices.
  </p>

  <p>
    Currently, I work as a <strong><%= currentRole %></strong>, leading a team
    of <strong><%= teamSize %></strong> engineers. I handle the complete
    lifecycle — from system design and component architecture to performance
    optimization and deployment.
  </p>

  <p>
    I specialize in developing maintainable, scalable React applications with a
    strong focus on performance, reusability, and clean architecture.
  </p>

  <p>
    I’m seeking new opportunities due to
    <strong>location constraints</strong> and a strong desire for
    <strong>career growth</strong> and
    <strong>professional development</strong>.
  </p>

  <div
    style="
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    "
  >
    <p style="margin-top: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #0f172a">Key Details:</p>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px">
      <li><strong>Total Experience:</strong> <%= experienceYears %> years</li>
      <li><strong>Current Role:</strong> <%= currentRole %></li>
      <li>
        <strong>Key Skills:</strong> React, Next.js, Redux, TypeScript, REST
        APIs, UI/UX, System Design
      </li>
      <li><strong>Current CTC:</strong> <%= currentCtc %></li>
      <li><strong>Expected CTC:</strong> <%= expectedCtc %></li>
      <li>
        <strong>Notice Period:</strong> <%= noticePeriod || 'Immediate' %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Availability:</strong>
        <span style="color: #047857">Immediate Joining</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>
    You can review my work and background here:<br />
    <% if (typeof portfolioUrl !== 'undefined' && portfolioUrl) { %> 🌐
    Portfolio:
    <a href="<%= portfolioUrl %>" style="color: #2563eb"><%= portfolioUrl %></a
    ><br />
    <% } %> <% if (typeof linkedInUrl !== 'undefined' && linkedInUrl) { %> 💼
    LinkedIn:
    <a href="<%= linkedInUrl %>" style="color: #2563eb"><%= linkedInUrl %></a
    ><br />
    <% } %> <% if (typeof githubUrl !== 'undefined' && githubUrl) { %> 🧑‍💻
    GitHub:
    <a href="<%= githubUrl %>" style="color: #2563eb"><%= githubUrl %></a><br />
    <% } %> <% if (typeof resumeUrl !== 'undefined' && resumeUrl) { %> 📄
    Resume:
    <a href="<%= resumeUrl %>" style="color: #2563eb"><%= resumeUrl %></a>
    <% } %>
  </p>

  <p>
    I’m available for immediate joining and would be happy to discuss how I can
    contribute to your team. Thank you for considering my application.
  </p>

  <div
    style="
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
    "
  >
    <p style="margin: 0">
      Regards,<br />
      <strong><%= senderName %></strong><br />
      📞
      <a href="tel:<%= phone %>" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none"
        ><%= phone %></a
      ><br />
      📧
      <a
        href="mailto:<%= senderEmail %>"
        style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none"
        ><%= senderEmail %></a
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
